{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Drives macOS Setup Assistant automation by sending keyboard events"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a running "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"VZVirtualMachine"},{"type":"text","text":" through a "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/KeyboardDriver"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SetupAutomationExecutor"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SetupAutomationExecutor"},{"type":"text","text":" iterates over a sequence of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/BootStep","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"s,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"waiting for each step’s delay, then dispatching the keyboard action"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"through the provided "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/KeyboardDriver","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" implementation."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"How It Works","anchor":"How-It-Works","type":"heading","level":2},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The caller provides a "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/KeyboardDriver"},{"type":"text","text":" that knows how to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"deliver keyboard events to the VM (e.g., via an offscreen"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSWindow"},{"type":"text","text":" with a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"